Question: Are the glasses that are to the right of the remote control black or gold?

Reference Answer: The glasses are gold.

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n326988.jpg

Program:

```
 Are A <planar pos> B <attr> or <attr>?
Program:
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='remote control')
IMAGE0=CROP_RIGHTOF(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='glasses')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX1)
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'black' if {ANSWER0} > 0 else 'gold'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
